Hi there..

Please read this whole introduction to the end.

A while ago, I started to upload a version of this word for word movie of the accounts of John in the Bible. And on request, I started to track down a Spanish-subbed version.

I found one, but the subs weren't very good, according to Spanish feedback. So I got me a copy of the original movie, ripped it in the three available subtitles and languages; Spanish, French and English.

I decided that a English subbed version would be great for the hearing-impaired in the English speaking countries.

So this is the result.

